Sentencas: This study investigated the effects of the apparent thickness of porous Pt cathode thin films thermo-mechanically stabilized by an atomic layer-deposited (ALD) alumina capping agent on effective electrical conductivity and electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Thickness determination of porous Pt cathode thin film capped by atomic layer-deposited alumina for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Four-point probe resistance measurements revealed that a 120 nm-thick porous Pt film exhibits a relatively high electrical conductivity of 9.2 x 10(3) S/cm.
Titulo: Thickness determination of porous Pt cathode thin film capped by atomic layer-deposited alumina for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Cathode reaction resistance measurements by means of alternating current impedance spectroscopy (ACIS) analysis show that ALD alumina can act as a thermo-mechanical stabilizer for a 120 nm-thick porous Pt cathode film.
Titulo: Thickness determination of porous Pt cathode thin film capped by atomic layer-deposited alumina for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The ACIS analysis results for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) with porous Pt cathode thin films of various thicknesses showed that a 120 nmthick porous Pt cathode film is thermo-mechanically stabilized by the conformal coating of an ALD alumina capping agent.
Titulo: Thickness determination of porous Pt cathode thin film capped by atomic layer-deposited alumina for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The iR-free polarization curves show that an ALD alumina-capped 120 nm porous Pt cathode film-embedded SOFC delivers similar to 65% higher power density than an ALD alumina-capped 480 nm-thick porous Pt cathode film-embedded SOFC.
Titulo: Thickness determination of porous Pt cathode thin film capped by atomic layer-deposited alumina for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
